==English==

===Etymology===
From [[ad]] a contraction of [[advertisement]] + [[ware]] a contraction of [[software]]

===Noun===
'''adware''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

#{{cattag|computing}}: A software [[application]] that includes advertisements, which are [[display]]ed while the software is running. Developers use adware as a source of [[income]] and to keep the [[cost]]s of the software down (usually making it free). Some adware [[program]]s can include spyware.

